"'That will do,' said he; 'I could not ask for anything better. Capital! capital!' He seemed quite
enthusiastic and rubbed his hands together in the most genial fashion. He was such a comfortable-
looking man that it was quite a pleasure to look at him.

"'You are looking for a situation, miss?' he asked.

"'Yes, sir.'

"'As governess?'

"'Yes, sir.'